<h3>URL Structure</h3>
<p>Clean URLs matter. Automotive sites often generate URLs like <code>/inventory/detail/123456789/2026-honda-cr-v</code>. Simplify where possible.</p>
<ul>
<li>Good: <code>/new-cars/2026-honda-cr-v</code></li>
<li>Bad: <code>/inventory/detail/VIN_1HGCV1F36RA000001</code></li>
<li>Good: <code>/service/oil-change-dallas</code></li>
<li>Bad: <code>/service?type=oil&amp;location=dallas</code></li>
</ul>
