<h3>Attribution for Automotive</h3>
<p>Car sales have a long attribution window. A buyer who reads your blog post in January may visit in March and purchase in April. Set up multi-touch attribution to track the full journey.</p>
<p>Use UTM parameters on all trackable links. Set up Google Analytics 4 conversion events for:</p>
<ul>
<li>Vehicle detail page views</li>
<li>Contact form submissions</li>
<li>Click-to-call actions</li>
<li>Directions requests (from GBP)</li>
<li>Chat initiations</li>
<li>Finance application starts</li>
</ul>
